Xz1RmWNmpg">Hàn than đãi phiếm kỳ 2 - 寒灘待泛其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng-S%C4%A9-Thuy%C3%AAn/Khai-Ti%C3%AAn-b%E1%BB%99c-b%E1%BB%91/poem-V8NLrnKAop8pgey0uChMFQ">Khai Tiên bộc bố - 開先瀑布</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng-S%C4%A9-Thuy%C3%AAn/author-W2mWmkTR4UigR3MuaZOlSg">Tưởng Sĩ Thuyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-t%E1%BA%B7ng-Qu%C3%A1ch-trung-th%E1%BB%ABa-ki%C3%AAm-th%C3%A1i-b%E1%BB%99c-khanh-sung-L%C5%A9ng-H%E1%BB%AFu-ti%E1%BA%BFt-%C4%91%E1%BB%99-s%E1%BB%A9-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-2XGzR8ArLA_7rTigSktnjQ">Phụng tặng Quách trung thừa kiêm thái bộc khanh sung Lũng Hữu tiết độ sứ tam thập vận - 奉送郭中丞兼太僕卿充隴右節度使三十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Long-C%C6%A1/Qu%E1%BB%B7-l%E1%BB%97i-ng%C3%A2m/poem-QNij4oLcYqqR3c_w1oTavw">Quỷ lỗi ngâm - 傀儡吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Long-C%C6%A1/author-LP68Aop4_S5Jf74CeC8Mjg">Lý Long Cơ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%E1%BA%A1ch-t%C3%AA-h%C3%A0nh/poem-xfZ_mXirWBP-Q9n6y0q8NQ">Thạch tê hành - 石犀行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-T%C3%ADch-K%E1%BB%B3/V%C5%A9-trung-qu%C3%A1-Th%E1%BA%A5t-L%C3%BD-lung-ca/poem-t1zljGkZZw_rj7vXYCTTVw">Vũ trung quá Thất Lý lung ca - 雨中過七里瀧歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-T%C3%ADch-K%E1%BB%B3/author-leXS2a46kBYHa9AoDh5zfw">Ngô Tích Kỳ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
